Class ObviousWekaUtils

java.lang.Object
  obviousx.io.weka.ObviousWekaUtils

public class ObviousWekaUtils
extends java.lang.Object

This class contains many static methods that allows to test if a Java type is numeric, a date, or nominal. It is usefull to create the convenient kind of Weka attributes.
